name: Trade Network
benefit: You may Trade with any player at any time.

name: Portable Forge
benefit: Gain 1 Legendary Artifact and 1 of any rune.

name: Fairy Intervention
benefit: After you roll incoming attack dice, you may reroll 1 of the incoming attack dice.

name: Shop Glitch
benefit: You may summon spirits from the shop with first priority, and all rarities below the rarity you were supposed to summon.

name: Saving Floral Patch
benefit: Once you have 4 unique Floral Patch Spirits, gain 3 Protector traits. Once you have 6 unique, you may summon your Floral Patch's mythic for free.

name: Saving Lantern Lights
benefit: Once you have 4 unique Lantern Lights Spirits, gain 3 Protector traits. Once you have 6 unique, you may summon your Lantern Lights's mythic for free.

name: Saving Tidal Tribe
benefit: Once you have 4 unique Tidal Tribe Spirits, gain 3 Protector traits. Once you have 6 unique, you may summon your Tidal Tribe's mythic for free.

name: Saving Arctic Nest
benefit: Once you have 4 unique Arctic Nest Spirits, gain 3 Protector traits. Once you have 6 unique, you may summon your Arctic Nest's mythic for free.

name: Saving Cyber City
benefit: Once you have 4 unique Cyber City Spirits, gain 3 Protector traits. Once you have 6 unique, you may summon your Cyber City's mythic for free.

name: Astral Gateway
benefit: If you Ascend or Recall, gain 1 barrier.

name: Cyber City Remnants
benefit: Gain 2 Cyber City runes

name: Astral Zone Remnants
benefit: Gain 1 Astral Zone runes

name: Void Remnants
benefit: Gain 1 Void runes

name: Twilight Fairies Remnants
benefit: Gain 1 Twilight Fairies runes

name: Underground Lights Remnants
benefit: Gain 2 Underground Lights runes

name: Floral Patch Remnants
benefit: Gain 2 Floral Patch runes

name: Tidal Tribe Remnants
benefit: Gain 2 Tidal Tribe runes

name: Arctic Nest Remnants
benefit: Gain 2 Arctic Nest runes

name: Advanced Weapons
benefit: Gain 1 Critical Attack per enemy in the Gather Phase.

name: Strategic Sacrifice
benefit: When you are about to loose a barrier, you may discard one of your Modern Human spirits to gain 2 barrier.

name: Tax Collector
benefit: Anytime you are on a location with multiple players, take 1 essense from those players.

name: Royal Prestige
benefit: Whenever you gain Victory Points, gain 2 more.

name: Particle Collector
benefit: If you move to a location more than 2 paths apart, such as through recall or animals, gain 1 Magic Dice

name: Regrowth
benefit: If you stay in your current location, gain 1 Barrier and 1 Ranged Attack

name: Battle Magic
benefit: Once you have gathered dice, you may gain 2 more of any of your current attack dice.

name: Cyber Attacks
benefit: Gain 1 Cyber Dice (or Magic Dice) per enemy in combat.

name: Art of War
benefit: Gain 3 breakpoint on any class.

name: Fairy-Scented Candle
benefit: Anytime you choose the Stay intent, gain 1 Exalted Attack and any 1 Rune.

name: Empty Space
benefit: If you are the only person on a location, gain 1 Barrier.

name: Floral Barrier
benefit: If you start combat with max barrier, gain 3 defense per opponent in combat.

name: Quantum Scopes
benefit: Gain 2+ breakpoint for Archers and Sorcerers

name: Arcane Master
benefit: Gain 1 Arcane Magic Dice in every Gather phase.

name: Void Barrier
benefit: You may deflect 1 dice after the Distribute Phase.
